" id=\"breadcrumbs\"> <h1> <span>Breadcrumbs</span> </h1> </nav> <div class=\"portlet-boundary portlet-boundary_103_ portlet-static portlet-static-end \" id=\"p_p_id_103_\" > <span id=\"p_103\"></span> <div class=\"portlet-body\"> </div> </div> <div class=\"columns-2\" id=\"main-content\" role=\"main\"> <div class=\"portlet-layout\"> <div class=\"aui-left-fix portlet-column portlet-column-first\" id=\"column-1\"> <div class=\"portlet-dropzone portlet-column-content portlet-column-content-first\" id=\"layout-column_column-1\"> <div class=\"portlet-boundary portlet-boundary_71_ portlet-static portlet-static-end portlet-borderless portlet-navigation \" id=\"p_p_id_71_INSTANCE_GDReHHoHMQo7_\" > <span id=\"p_71_INSTANCE_GDReHHoHMQo7\"></span> <div class=\"portlet-body\"> <div class=\"portlet-borderless-container\" style=\"\"> <div class=\"portlet-body\"> <div class=\"nav-menu nav-menu-style-none\"> <ul class=\"layouts level-1\"><li class=\"\" ><a class=\"\" href=\"&#x2f;html&#x2f;belgocontrol_static&#x2f;eaip&#x2f;eAIP_Product&#x2f;index&#x2e;html\" target=\"_blank\"> AIP - effective</a></li><li class=\"\" ><a class=\"\" href=\"&#x2f;html&#x2f;belgocontrol_static&#x2f;eaip_upcoming&#x2f;eAIP_Product&#x2f;index&#x2e;html\" target=\"_blank\"> AIP - upcoming</a></li><li class=\"\" ><a class=\"\" href=\"https&#x3a;&#x2f;&#x2f;ops&#x2e;skeyes&#x2e;be&#x2f;oper-preflight-briefing\" > Preflight Information</a></li><li class=\"selected \" ><a class=\"selected \" href=\"https&#x3a;&#x2f;&#x2f;ops&#x2e;skeyes&#x2e;be&#x2f;oper-meteo-info\" > Meteo Information</a></li><li class=\"\" ><a class=\"\" href=\"https&#x3a;&#x2f;&#x2f;ops&#x2e;skeyes&#x2e;be&#x2f;oper-flight-planning\" > Flight Planning</a></li><li class=\"\" ><a class=\"\" href=\"&#x2f;PilotBriefingWeb\" target=\"_blank\"> Handler Briefing</a></li><li class=\"\" ><a class=\"\" href=\"https&#x3a;&#x2f;&#x2f;ops&#x2e;skeyes&#x2e;be&#x2f;oper-notam-provider\" > Aero Data Provision</a></li></ul> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class=\"aui-right-float portlet-column portlet-column-last\" id=\"column-2\"> <div class=\"portlet-dropzone portlet-column-content portlet-column-content-last\" id=\"layout-column_column-2\"> <div class=\"portlet-boundary portlet-boundary_56_ portlet-static portlet-static-end portlet-journal-content \" id=\"p_p_id_56_INSTANCE_fPs0tMDvZufg_\" > <span id=\"p_56_INSTANCE_fPs0tMDvZufg\"></span> <div class=\"portlet-body\"> <section class=\"portlet\" id=\"portlet_56_INSTANCE_fPs0tMDvZufg\"> <header class=\"portlet-topper\"> <h1 class=\"portlet-title\"> <span class=\"portlet-title-text\"></span> </h1> <menu class=\"portlet-topper-toolbar\" id=\"portlet-topper-toolbar_56_INSTANCE_fPs0tMDvZufg\" type=\"toolbar\"> </menu> </header> <div class=\"portlet-content\"> <div class=\" portlet-content-container\" style=\"\"> <div class=\"portlet-body\"> <div class=\"journal-content-article\"> <div class=\"belgo-journal-template\"> <!--<div class=\"contact\" style=\"max-width: 800px\"> <span>Message </span> <div class=\"contactinfo\" style=\"color: red\"> On Wednesday 2 April between 18h00 and 19h00 LT the AIM/METEO Briefing and HANDLER Briefing will be temporarily unavailable. Everything will be done to limit the interruption to the bare minimum. We apologize for this inconvenience.</div> </div> <br /> <p> &nbsp;</p>--> <div class=\"contact\" style=\"max-width: 800px\"> <span>Message </span> <div class=\"contactinfo\" style=\"color: red\"> We are currently in the process of renewing/replacing our weather radar. During this time there are no images of the Brussels weather radar available. In the meantime and as an alternative the images from RMIB (radar sites at Jabbeke and Wideumont) and a composite of European weather radars will be available.</div> <br /> <p> &nbsp;</p> </div> </div> </div> <div class=\"entry-links\"> </div> </div> </div> </div> </section> </div> </div> <div class=\"portlet-boundary portlet-boundary_48_ portlet-static portlet-static-end portlet-iframe \" id=\"p_p_id_48_INSTANCE_6F0tHgAgzQdu_\" > <span id=\"p_48_INSTANCE_6F0tHgAgzQdu\"></span> <div class=\"portlet-body\"> <section class=\"portlet\" id=\"portlet_48_INSTANCE_6F0tHgAgzQdu\"> <header class=\"portlet-topper\"> <h1 class=\"portlet-title\"> <span class=\"portlet-title-text\">Meteo Information</span> </h1> <menu class=\"portlet-topper-toolbar\" id=\"portlet-topper-toolbar_48_INSTANCE_6F0tHgAgzQdu\" type=\"toolbar\"> </menu> </header> <div class=\"portlet-content\"> <div class=\" portlet-content-container\" style=\"\"> <div class=\"portlet-body\"> <div> <iframe alt=\"\" border=\"0\" bordercolor=\"#000000\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"800\" hspace=\"0\" id=\"_48_INSTANCE_6F0tHgAgzQdu_iframe\" longdesc=\"\" name=\"_48_INSTANCE_6F0tHgAgzQdu_iframe\" onload=\"_48_INSTANCE_6F0tHgAgzQdu_monitorIframe();\" scrolling=\"auto\" src=\"/opersite/opmeteoindex.do?cmd=init&\" title=\"\" vspace=\"0\" width=\"100%\"> Your browser does not support inline frames or is currently configured not to display inline frames. Content can be viewed at actual source page: /opersite/opmeteoindex.do?cmd=init&. </iframe> </div> </div> </div> </div> </section> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class=\"portlet-boundary portlet-boundary_gdprportlet_WAR_gdprportlet_ portlet-static portlet-static-end gdpr-portlet \" id=\"p_p_id_gdprportlet_WAR_gdprportlet_\" > <span id=\"p_gdprportlet_WAR_gdprportlet\"></span> <div class=\"portlet-body\"> <portlet:defineObjects /> <div id=\"gdpr\" class=\"gdpr\"> </div> </div> </div> <form action=\"#\" id=\"hrefFm\" method=\"post\" name=\"hrefFm\"> <span></span> </form> </div> <footer id=\"footer\" role=\"contentinfo\"> <div id=\"footer-container\"> <div class=\"belgo-journal-template\"> <section class=\"footer-section\"> <h1> OUR OTHER WEBSITES</h1> <ul> <li> <a href=\"https://www.skeyes.be\">Corporate website</a></li> <li> <a href=\"https://www.batc.be\">Brussels Airport Traffic Control</a></li> <li> <a href=\"https://www.skeyes.be/en